* /fbapp/{appId}/ FacebookAppServer.load
* /load/app/{appId}/ FacebookAppServer.load
POST /campaign/{campaignId}/ RuntimeServer.post
POST /campaign/{campaignId}/vote RuntimeServer.voteEntry
